trans-unit.source: This data comes from the KDD Cup 2010 Student performance evaluation challenge (student performance evaluation).
trans-unit.target: This data comes from the KDD Cup 2010 Student performance evaluation challenge (student performance evaluation).

trans-unit.source: The data used is the Algebra_2008_2009 training set (Stamper, J., Niculescu-Mizil, A., Ritter, S., Gordon, G.J., & Koedinger, K.R.
trans-unit.target: The data used is the Algebra_2008_2009 training set (Stamper, J., Niculescu-Mizil, A., Ritter, S., Gordon, G.J., & Koedinger, K.R.

trans-unit.source: Challenge data set from KDD Cup 2010 Educational Data Mining Challenge.
trans-unit.target: Challenge data set from KDD Cup 2010 Educational Data Mining Challenge.

trans-unit.source: The dataset was downloaded and stored in Azure Blob storage (student_performance.txt) and contains log files from a student tutoring system.
trans-unit.target: The dataset was downloaded and stored in Azure Blob storage (student_performance.txt) and contains log files from a student tutoring system.

trans-unit.source: The supplied features include problem ID and its brief description, student ID, timestamp, and how many attempts the student made before solving the problem in the right way.
trans-unit.target: The supplied features include problem ID and its brief description, student ID, timestamp, and how many attempts the student made before solving the problem in the right way.

trans-unit.source: The original dataset has 8.9M records, this dataset has been down-sampled to the first 100K rows.
trans-unit.target: The original dataset has 8.9M records, this dataset has been down-sampled to the first 100K rows.

trans-unit.source: The dataset has 23 tab-separated columns of various types: numeric, categorical, and timestamp.
trans-unit.target: The dataset has 23 tab-separated columns of various types: numeric, categorical, and timestamp.
